. The non-negativity 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha\geq 0$
\end_inset

 is guaranteed by 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_1<0$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\chi>0$
\end_inset

. 
\end_layout

