\begin_inset Formula \begin{align*}
\HV y_2 &= \alpha_{12}(y_1-y_2) + \alpha_{23}(y_3-y_2), \\
(-a\lambda_1,\,-\tfrac{h}{2}\lambda_2)^\intercal &= (a\alpha_{12}+2a\alpha_{23},\;\tfrac{3h}{2}\alpha_{12})^\intercal,
\end{align*}
\end_inset

giving 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha_{23}=\frac{\lambda_2}{6}-\frac{\lambda_1}{2}$
\end_inset

. The constraint 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha_{23}\geq 0$
\end_inset

 requires 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_2\geq 3\lambda_1$
\end_inset

, i.e., 
\begin_inset Formula $|\lambda_2|/|\lambda_1|\geq 3$
\end_inset

. 
